Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.47,0:25:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果玉玲死掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.94,0:25:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥就會孤單一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.81,0:25:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.61,0:25:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.78,0:25:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃一點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.35,0:25:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吃啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.15,0:25:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.49,0:25:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.69,0:25:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.27,0:25:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.38,0:26:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.32,0:26:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.29,0:26:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一點都沒變…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.80,0:26:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然記憶都已經消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.03,0:26:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何那種損己利人的個性還在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.58,0:26:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.04,0:26:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡那樣的玉玲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.08,0:26:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.38,0:26:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會讓玉玲送死的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.89,0:26:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭目，螃蟹不合妳的胃口嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.69,0:26:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.20,0:27:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.00,0:27:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個味道我好像在哪裡吃過…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.10,0:27:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯…\N是小時候很懷念的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.77,0:27:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們用純真無邪的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.24,0:27:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕鬆相視而笑的Sweet Days
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.18,0:27:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,街景已不復以往
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.31,0:27:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在我倆仍相伴左右
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.75,0:27:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是未來的際遇卻很難說
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.45,0:28:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連老天爺都無法捉摸
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.29,0:28:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融進迎面吹來的風裡walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.33,0:28:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無數顆future之星
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.97,0:28:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜悄悄的被鑲在無涯的天空裡
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.81,0:28:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交疊的溫熱維繫着一切閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.41,0:28:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充斥着無法實現的諾言
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.32,0:28:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界漸漸沉淪墮落
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.52,0:28:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kissing till l die
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.22,0:28:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力掩蓋傷痕 創造永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.99,0:28:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在危機之中讓我們相愛
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.66,0:28:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So，也許是我倆的生存方式come on！
